The core JayVee library provides the fundamental copmonents of JayVee. Primarily, it provides the basic workflow system which is the foundation for the entire JayVee architecture. Familiarity with this system is highly recommended for any developer using JayVee.

In addition, this library provides the base Image interface which is used throughout JayVee. This library also provides basic routines for I/O and simple image transformations.
